/*******************************************************************************

    Home Site ...... http://enterprise.huawei.com
    Program ........ Huawei server plugin for Cacti
    Version ........ 1.0
    Purpose ........ View/Manage Huawei server informations from Cacti

*******************************************************************************/


----[ Purpose

    This plugin is used to communicate with Huawei iBMC and HMM through SNMP protocol to
     get the server os & hardware information, and present it.


----[ Features

    View total 15 categories of Huawei server informations.
    Related device and graph templates, to present the performance chart of Huawei server.


----[ Installation

    Install just like any other plugin, just throw it in the plugin directory,
    in a folder called huawei-server.


----[ Possible Bugs?

    If you figure out this problem, let me know!!!


----[ Future Changes

    Integrate with cacti threshold plugin to support monitor and warning of Huawei server!


